:: Opening_5
"Wake up," a rough voice awoke you from your nap. "Take your dinner, slave."

You blink blearily as the sound of another wooden plate scraping across the ground echoes \
around you.

You stand to collect your food- "Wait." The food is pulled back out.

"Pass me the other plate first."

